{"tid":1523983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好撚嬲嘅同我入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-31T16:29:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T01:21:34.000Z","uid":111982,"like":176,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"010d511610a91c9ead1b825cc9994f7055b7643d","tid":1523983,"uid":111982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:29:18.000Z","msg":"我都好撚嬲<br />\n<br />\n【突發！】記者左眼中彈！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1522301\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1522301</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n有兩條片影到掉汽油彈嘅，背囊有閃燈<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1522846\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1522846</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n維園開左真槍！有圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1522876\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1522876</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n831 太子黑警恐襲高清影片<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1523520\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1523520</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n可以點做？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全 部 同 我 入 機 場！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n［重要］901 機場懶人包/指南/玩法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1522857\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1522857</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tiZgOco.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtiZgOco.png&h=feb132a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a78e9a01e8d959ea72ab5a1bf2a396d10bc1f157","tid":1523983,"uid":227275,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:29:44.000Z","msg":"跳閘仲好喇 賺返轉頭<br />\n到時風氣流行左就好似歐洲咁 成堆人唔比錢<br />\n大家可以慣左黑警亂打人 都可以慣左跳閘<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>清洗每個狗鐵站 拆鐵行動! 旺角行先!</strong></span></span><br />\n明明你地有能力 又咁容易 點解大家仲未收狗鐵皮?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1523278\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1523278</a>"},{"pid":"612c93b1ea0dd7ce0f8e0f20d4ef884e